Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.01,0:00:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{Death incarnate, huh?}Thần chết à??
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.11,0:01:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{Mother, Father, how are you faring?}Thưa bố, mẹ, chuyến đi của bố mẹ như thế nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.21,0:01:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{I remain, as always, a lost cause.}Con vẫn thế, rất phiền toái
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.00,0:01:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{This curse, which takes\Nthe life of anything I touch,}cái lời nguyền có thể lấy đi sinh mạng của những gì con chạm vào này.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.05,0:01:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{shows no signs of breaking.}Không có dâu hiệu rằng sẽ biến mất.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.09,0:01:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{My Lady, another animal\Ntouched the boy and...}Thưa cô chủ, lại một con vật khác được cậu Bocchan chạm vào và...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.63,0:01:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{Living under the same roof\Nas him makes me livid with fear!}Sống chung nhà với thằng bé này khiên ta chết lặng.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.97,0:01:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{Send him to our villa.}Hãy gửi nó đếnh dinh thự.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.02,0:01:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{That child is like Death incarnate...}Cứ như là đứa con của thần chết 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.06,0:01:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{Why did the witch put this curse on me?}Tại sao phù thủy lại đặt lời nguyền này lên con?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{There is something else that troubles me.}Có một sứ làm con phiền lòng ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{And that is...}và đó là....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{Your Grace, your tea is ready.}bocchan, trà của ngài đã chuẩn bị xong rồi ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{Don't stand so close to me!}Gần quá đấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.01,0:03:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Tập 1: Công tước and và Alice"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.73,0:03:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to send that letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:04:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't written a letter in so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It was for practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My maid's name is Alice. I have no\Nidea what goes on in her head.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She knows if I touch her,\Nshe'll die, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.63,0:04:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rather chilly today, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She says one thing and does the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.05,0:04:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Every day she tries to get a rise out\Nof me, and then watches how I react.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Your Grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.06,0:04:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.77,0:04:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you wanted me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't drop my head\Ndown to see up your skirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep telling you to lay off\Nthe sexual harassment!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.74,0:04:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes it hard for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.37,0:04:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're awfully sure about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.38,0:04:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You should put your own safety first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.29,0:05:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one maid who'll stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.72,0:05:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to lose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what I mean to you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.27,0:05:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How about another cookie?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.69,0:05:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Up to the part where you said,\N"I don't know what I mean to you, but..."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you heard all of it!\NAnd you just ignored me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still one left.\NPlease clean your plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make weird noises!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.55,0:05:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That was an indirect kiss, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.18,0:05:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to say\Nthat out loud, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I take the life of anything I touch...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A witch put this curse\Non me when I was five.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.41,0:06:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who she was, where she\Ncame from, or why she did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...my memory fails me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"No one shall love you,\Nand you shall love no one."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"You shall live a life of misery."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All I remember are the witch's words.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Turning her back on me, my mother\Ngave me this mansion in the forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and I haven't seen my family since.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I could break the curse,\NI could go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,To the home where I belong...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Your Grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice! N-Not this again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.02,0:07:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to lay off\Nthe sexual harassment!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.31,0:07:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You always react so innocently. It makes\Nme want to tease you all the more!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice is the only daughter of the head\Nmaid at my family's residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.36,0:07:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I've known her since she was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I hadn't seen her for a while,\Nuntil about two years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.71,0:07:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,when for reasons I don't\Nunderstand, she came here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.62,0:07:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't make me feel better!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:07:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You stopped, then started again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice, cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not look like it,\Nbut I'm a man, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.27,0:08:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I give into temptation\Nand touch you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to touch me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.28,0:08:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop toying with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.55,0:08:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you have to get so close?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What if you touched me accidentally?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She saw the weird faces\NI make in my sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought you your breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not hungry. And there's way too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.11,0:08:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you said when\Nyou skipped dinner last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother used to insist that you eat\Nthree square meals a day, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not fair of you to\Nbring up my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.92,0:09:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What if you should fall ill...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.75,0:09:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...and never be able to spend your\Nnights fooling around with me again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Spend my nights doing what with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true, I do feel bad that I never\Nfinish the food you make me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can eat a little, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, say aah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You really want to feed me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She's staring at the inside of my mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I don't get many\Nchances to see inside your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,--I couldn't help it.\N--Well, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.33,0:09:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,As an apology, would you care\Nto have a look inside my mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.38,0:09:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You don't have to show it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.84,0:09:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll eat on my own.\NHand me the fork.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Grace, why are you\Nso uninterested in eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Because ever since I was cursed,\Nmealtimes were the worst part of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been slow, but ever since you\Ncame here, I've started to eat more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful, even if I don't look it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.42,0:10:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll clear away these dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Grace, your childhood friend\NPhilip says he'd like to see you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,as it's been too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, it seems that Philip\Nwas here just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.37,0:11:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's none of your concern, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I told him I'd see him, but now that\Nthe day is here, I'm getting cold feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it too late to refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.49,0:11:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Send him a letter saying\NI can't meet today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late for that. Just accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.08,0:11:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember Philip?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. He was a lively young boy,\Nvery unusual for a noble's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He used to chase you around\Nwith a snake in his hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...or throw bugs at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he was a bit of a troublemaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.93,0:12:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...you're looking forward\Nto meeting him, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,H-H-Hello there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.56,0:12:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't peek inside my room!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.81,0:12:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's been so long\Nsince we've had guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll change into my formal attire.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.86,0:12:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. I'll take your\Ntuxedo out of storage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, about that hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm absolutely,\Npositively not taking it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My naturally curly hair and these circles\Nunder my eyes make me look so uncool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to hide them with a hat, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You have hair that people love to curl\Naround their fingers, mysterious eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and such kissable lips...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get your tuxedo ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.78,0:13:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Will this do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You can leave while I change.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.16,0:13:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can change on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.25,0:13:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take my clothes off\Nin front of a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.12,0:13:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you feel less self-conscious\Nif we both took our clothes off?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.67,0:13:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't start taking your\Nclothes off, I'll take mine off first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.17,0:13:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of threat is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I'm a little\Nhopeful about today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I gathered as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.73,0:13:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you don't touch me directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was cursed, and my family\Nand friends all started to avoid me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,he was the one person\Nwho looked at me differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:13:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never forgotten that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that the day is here, I feel\Nnervous about meeting him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.55,0:14:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...if he's willing to give\Nme another chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,perhaps we can be friends again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put your tie on, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't yell into my ear, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.48,0:14:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't behave like this\Nwhen Philip is around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't want another man\Nto see your bare skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I only do it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I see.\NThen, I guess that's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.34,0:14:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only fun if I get\Nto see your reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Scratch that! It's not okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.93,0:14:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hello there, Philip.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:14:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah. Thanks for having me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.06,0:14:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How many years has it been?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to throw\Nbugs at me, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Bugs? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten? You used to\Nplay all kinds of pranks on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You've really mellowed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so long ago\NI don't remember it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, it's not that I wanted\Nyou to apologize...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.25,0:15:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.21,0:15:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just... um... making a cool pose!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.90,0:15:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that I'd gotten my hopes\Nup only makes it feel worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do you want, Philip?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, um... It's nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to see an old friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, aren't you the daughter\Nof the family's head maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. You remembered me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.43,0:16:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I remember you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you working here as a maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it just the two of you living here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally I have a butler as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.35,0:16:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He hurt his back and is resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But he'll be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Grace!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.13,0:16:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We're fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you leaving so soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.23,0:17:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We've talked enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.11,0:17:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, where is the lavatory?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.36,0:17:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.80,0:17:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.67,0:17:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you come back to town with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous for you to stay with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find you another job, if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You must leave this place at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.69,0:17:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.65,0:17:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Has he threatened you? Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Philip!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say anything that\Nwould cause her trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:18:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You can disrespect me all\Nyou want, but not Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.58,0:18:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Grace, please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come near me, you monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I didn't even want to come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.73,0:18:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother wanted me\Nto see how you were doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.98,0:18:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There's talk of having your younger\Nbrother inherit the family title.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.41,0:18:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing your family, if that happens,\Nthey'll cut off ties with you entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.41,0:18:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.62,0:18:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay. I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be scared of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:18:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but I pity you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.39,0:19:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Telling you the truth is\Nmy way of making amends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.68,0:19:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.43,0:19:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never come back here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.24,0:19:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Grace...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm totally fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.46,0:19:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just forget about it\Nand have dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.92,0:19:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me know when it's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so good at the piano...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.94,0:19:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play again sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll always be buddies!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.08,0:20:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This curse will be broken...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Or it won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.91,0:20:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My family will accept me again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.83,0:20:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Or they won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.63,0:20:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice loves me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She loves me not...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.47,0:20:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Dinner is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.06,0:20:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.02,0:20:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.65,0:20:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a lost cause...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.57,0:20:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever you're away, I always think about\Nthings that make me feel ill at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.45,0:20:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My past self. My future self.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And my present self.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.58,0:20:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got no confidence in anything.\NI bet you hate me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.21,0:21:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I don't even\Nhave the right to love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.51,0:21:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't touch you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.05,0:21:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never know the heat of another's\Nbody nor the warmth of their tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If I wanted to give you a present...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.77,0:21:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...even a flower, it will just\Nwilt in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.07,0:21:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Philip was right. I'll never go back\Nto the house I grew up in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.40,0:21:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll remain a monster that everyone\Nhas turned their back on--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.57,0:21:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.41,0:21:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.16,0:21:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In the language of flowers,\Na wilted white rose means
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.08,0:21:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"to swear your whole life to someone."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.30,0:21:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is more than enough\Nof a present for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.30,0:21:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's break your curse together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.73,0:21:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.44,0:22:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'd like to put a ring on your\Nfinger with my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.51,0:23:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.51,0:23:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. There's no sign of\Nthe curse being broken,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.01,0:23:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but he seems to be\Nleading a peaceful life.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.43,0:23:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.93,0:23:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You may leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.65,0:23:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for such a wonderful meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.99,0:23:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You ate quite a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.57,0:23:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I guess it's because\NI was feeling kind of tense today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.29,0:23:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.42,0:23:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,thanks for always making\Nsuch delicious meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.55,0:23:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go on making them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.47,0:23:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Breakfast, lunch, and dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.97,0:23:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for you, Your Grace. Always.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.48,0:24:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"The Duke of Death and His Maid"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.48,0:24:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The Duke, His Butler, and a Lost Cat.
